ru Douglas Crockford</a> in this <a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/issues/3057">Bootstrap issue from back in the day</a>;</p>\n<blockquote><p>That is insanely stupid code. I am not going to dumb down JSMin for this case.</p></blockquote>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href="http://blog.futtta.be/2014/08/18/when-should-you-trycatch-javascript/" rel="bookmark" title="(When) should you Try/Catch Javascript?">(When) should you Try/Catch Javascript? </a></li>\n<li><a href="http://blog.futtta.be/2014/02/13/should-you-inline-or-defer-blocking-css/" rel="bookmark" title="Should you inline or defer blocking CSS?">Should you inline or defer blocking CSS? </a></li>\n<li><a href="http://blog.futtta.be/2015/05/20/is-your-string-zipped/" rel="bookmark" title="Is your string zipped?">Is your string zipped? </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_wordpress/~4/pcWQBr4AyA8" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"http://blog.futtta.be/2016/03/30/about-insanely-stupid-code/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://blog.futtta.be/2016/03/30/about-insanely-stupid-code/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:60:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8: