pre class="brush:vb;ruler: true">Dim dateTime:Set dateTime=DotNetFactory.CreateInstance("System.DateTime")\r\n\r\nMsgbox dateTime.Now.ToString("MMM ddd d HH:mm yyyy")\r\n</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Getting Short and Long Date</h4>\r\n<pre class="brush:vb;ruler: true">Msgbox dateTime.Now.ToLongDateString()\'Long date\r\n\r\nMsgbox dateTime.Now.ToShortDateString()\'Short date\r\n</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Displaying AM or PM FROM a date</h4>\r\n<pre class="brush:vb;ruler: true">Msgbox dateTime.Now.ToString("tt ")\r\n\'The output will be AM or PM\r\n</pre>', 'Date and Time', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '197-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-11 14:40:41', '2016-03-11 14:40:41', '', 197, 'http://www.codoid.com/197-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
