INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_f0npwq3mss_posts` VALUES (450, 1, '2016-05-24 05:04:34', '2016-05-24 05:04:34', 'Though industry has more approaches and frameworks for web application automation testing, but Codoid\'s framework setup, scripting best practices &amp; standards and object locating strategy are different and reduce false positives.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.codoid.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/web-automation-testing.png" alt=\'web automation testing\'></img>', 'Web Apps Automation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-24 05:04:34', '2016-05-24 05:04:34', '', 24, 'http://www.codoid.com/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_f0npwq3mss_posts` VALUES (451, 1, '2016-05-24 05:24:08', '2016-05-24 05:24:08', 'Though industry has more approaches and frameworks for web application automation testing, but Codoid\'s framework setup, scripting best practices &amp; standards and object locating strategy are different and reduce false positives.\r\n\r\nWriting an automated test script is an easy job; it can be done by anyone who has limited knowledge in automation testing, but thinking about script maintenance, following up best practices, using right framework and tool are very important aspects. We, at Codoid, know how to create reliable and maintainable test scripts which can be used for longer run without modifications unless there is no UI or functionality change.   \r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.codoid.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/web-automation-testing.png" alt=\'web automation testing\'></img>', 'Web Apps Automation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-24 05:24:08', '2016-05-24 05:24:08', '', 24, 'http://www.codoid.com/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_f0npwq3mss_posts` VALUES (452, 1, '2016-05-24 05:26:22', '2016-05-24 05:26:22', 'Whether it is an open source or commercial mobile automation tool, mobile test scripts are difficult to update and maintain. From our experience, a successful mobile automation project is not an easy task even if we have very good frameworks, infrastructure and resources.\r\n\r\nMobile automation testing is not matured enough and most experts are improving mobile automation tools and implementation. We always encourage our customers to take measured steps with mobile automation projects. For us, script maintenance and result are important than script development.\r\n\r\nAs an automation testing services company, we have our own mobile automation framework, process and talented people to reduce false positives as much as possible for mobile automation testing.\r\n\r\n<img src=\'http://www.codoid.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/mobile-automation-testing.png\' alt=\'mobile automation testing\'></img>', 'Mobile Automation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '28-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-24 05:26:22', '2016-05-24 05:26:22', '', 28, 'http://www.codoid.com/28-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
